## Task

Implement RSS feed generation for the nav-site to allow users to subscribe to link updates via feed readers.

## Problem

The current nav-site has no RSS feed, which means:
- Users cannot subscribe to link updates via feed readers
- No automated way to track new links or changes
- Missing standard web feature for content discovery
- Reduced accessibility for RSS-focused users
- No integration with IFTTT, Zapier, or other automation tools
- Poor support for aggregate/link blog use cases

## Proposed Solution

Implement RSS 2.0 feed generation with Express middleware:

